Package org.emoncms.http

Class HttpFeed

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.emoncms.http.HttpFeed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Feed
    public class HttpFeed
extends java.lang.Object
implements Feed
    The HttpFeed implementation provides the Emoncms interface for HTTP feed requests. Feeds hold all their configuration fields in memory, but may be cleared to only hold their ID by calling clear(). Feed methods only need the ID to maintain their functionality and other resources may be released to save memory. Current values for all fields can be retrieved by calling load().
